# GSAP

## Setup

```js
import gsap from "gsap"
import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger"
gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger)
```

## Core API

```js
// FROM — anima dos valores fornecidos até o estado atual
gsap.from(".hero h1", { y: 40, opacity: 0, duration: 0.8, ease: "expo.out" })

// TO — anima até os valores fornecidos
gsap.to(".box", { x: 200, rotation: 45, duration: 1 })

// FROMTO — início e fim explícitos
gsap.fromTo(".card", { opacity: 0, y: 30 }, { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.6 })
```

## Timeline — sequenciar animações

```js
const tl = gsap.timeline({ delay: 0.2 })
tl.from("nav",  { y: -60, opacity: 0, duration: 0.5 })
  .from("h1",   { y: 30,  opacity: 0, duration: 0.7 }, "-=0.2")
  .from("p",    { y: 20,  opacity: 0, duration: 0.5 }, "-=0.3")
  .from(".cta", { scale: 0.9, opacity: 0, duration: 0.4 }, "-=0.2")
```

## ScrollTrigger

```js
// Scroll reveal básico
gsap.from(".section", {
  scrollTrigger: {
    trigger: ".section",
    start: "top 85%",
    toggleActions: "play none none reverse"
  },
  y: 50, opacity: 0, duration: 0.8
})

// Stagger no scroll
gsap.from(".card", {
  scrollTrigger: { trigger: ".cards-grid", start: "top 75%" },
  y: 40, opacity: 0, stagger: 0.1, duration: 0.6, ease: "power2.out"
})

// Scrub — animação vinculada à posição do scroll
gsap.to(".parallax-img", {
  scrollTrigger: {
    trigger: ".parallax-section",
    start: "top bottom", end: "bottom top",
    scrub: 1
  },
  y: -100
})

// Batch — performance para muitos elementos
ScrollTrigger.batch(".item", {
  onEnter: (elements) => gsap.from(elements, {
    opacity: 0, y: 30, stagger: 0.08, duration: 0.6
  }),
  start: "top 90%"
})
```

## Custom Cursor

```astro
<div id="cursor"></div>
<div id="cursor-dot"></div>

<style>
  #cursor {
    position: fixed; width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
  #cursor-dot {
    position: fixed; width: 4px; height: 4px;
    background: white; border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
</style>

<script>
  import gsap from "gsap"
  const cursor = document.getElementById("cursor")
  const dot = document.getElementById("cursor-dot")

  window.addEventListener("mousemove", (e) => {
    gsap.to(cursor, { x: e.clientX, y: e.clientY, duration: 0.4, ease: "power2.out" })
    gsap.to(dot, { x: e.clientX, y: e.clientY, duration: 0.1 })
  })

  document.querySelectorAll("a, button, [data-cursor-grow]").forEach(el => {
    el.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => gsap.to(cursor, { scale: 2.5, duration: 0.3 }))
    el.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => gsap.to(cursor, { scale: 1, duration: 0.3 }))
  })
</script>
```

## Magnetic Button

```astro
<button data-magnetic>Entrar em contato</button>

<script>
  import gsap from "gsap"
  document.querySelectorAll("[data-magnetic]").forEach(el => {
    el.addEventListener("mousemove", (e) => {
      const rect = el.getBoundingClientRect()
      const x = e.clientX - rect.left - rect.width / 2
      const y = e.clientY - rect.top - rect.height / 2
      gsap.to(el, { x: x * 0.3, y: y * 0.3, duration: 0.4, ease: "power2.out" })
    })
    el.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
      gsap.to(el, { x: 0, y: 0, duration: 0.5, ease: "elastic.out(1, 0.4)" })
    })
  })
</script>
```

## Text Reveal (sem plugin)

```js
const h1 = document.querySelector("h1")
const words = h1.textContent.split(" ").map(w => `<span style="display:inline-block">${w}</span>`)
h1.innerHTML = words.join(" ")
gsap.from(h1.querySelectorAll("span"), {
  y: 40, opacity: 0, stagger: 0.06, duration: 0.6, ease: "power2.out"
})
```

## Ease Reference

| Efeito | Ease |
|---|---|
| Entrada suave | `power2.out` |
| Entrada snappy | `expo.out` |
| Bounce | `elastic.out(1, 0.4)` |
| Saída | `power2.in` |
| Natural | `sine.inOut` |

